data.description:
Golf course living at its finest. Large roomy home located on Country Club Drive on hole #6...closest to the Golf Club Clubhouse. Have you been waiting for that perfect property to come on the market? Well your waiting is over!!! When entering this beautiful home you will find a beautiful HUGE family room with ceiling to floor windows lining the back of the home which looks over the fairway to hole #6….easy access through a pair of French doors to the back yard oasis equipped with a sunken hot tub. Watch the sun rise over the trees on your covered front porch….and watch the sun set from your massive back decks. The kitchen provides an abundance of storage and stainless steel appliances. Kitchen windows have flower boxes on the outside solidifying the charm of this massive home. There are 3 bedrooms and one bath on the first floor. Laundry room off the kitchen has a water softner. Primary bedroom upstairs has a bay window with sitting area, a large bath with double vanity, separate large tub and shower and his and her walk-in closets. There are French doors in this room that take you to an upstairs deck that overlooks the golf course lake…breathtaking views.  Just east of the kitchen is a setting room with wood like vinyl flooring and it has a built-in desk with good storage. The front room farthest from the kitchen is currently serving as a formal dining room. It once had a pool table and bar tables and chairs…so there are a lot of options with over 3000 sq. ft. 
When relaxing on the back patio…walk up to the club house and practice your putting on hole #6 that can be seen from this home. Because of the Low E windows throughout the home….and the insulation…the bills run lower than one would suspect. I could go on and on about this hidden treasure….I would love to buy it myself.
